flowchart TD
    A[Production Bug Reported] --> B{Triage: Severity?}
    B -->|Critical| C[Create Hotfix Branch]
    B -->|Major| D[Add to Next Sprint]
    B -->|Minor| E[Schedule Fix]
    
    C --> F[Implement Fix]
    F --> G[Local Testing]
    G --> H[Expedited Review]
    H --> I[Security Check]
    I --> J[Deploy to Staging]
    J --> K[Smoke Tests]
    K --> L{Pass?}
    L -->|Yes| M[Deploy to Production]
    L -->|No| N[Rollback & Debug]
    
    M --> O[Monitor 1 Hour]
    O --> P{Stable?}
    P -->|Yes| Q[Update Documentation]
    P -->|No| R[Rollback & Notify]
    
    Q --> S[Merge to Develop/Main]
    S --> T[Close Incident]
    
    style C fill:#FF4D4D
    style M fill:#00FF85
    style R fill:#FFB84D